# A multi-stop route for Nav2's waypoint follower / pass-through planner.
# Poses are parallel arrays (same length): the i-th stop is (xs[i], ys[i], thetas[i]),
# with thetas in degrees to match goToPose. mode selects the Nav2 action:
#   "through"   -> goThroughPoses  (one continuous pass, don't fully stop)
#   "waypoints" -> followWaypoints (visit each pose in turn)
float32[] xs
float32[] ys
float32[] thetas
string mode
---
string status
